SUMMARY:Spring Has Sprung! at Avana on Broad
DESCRIPTION:Thanks to Avana on Broad for hosting us for a meet-and-greet with adoptable dogs from APS! If you’re looking for a new furry friend\, or if you’re interested in volunteering or fostering with APS\, come and chat with us! Our fantastic volunteers will be on hand to help you out!
URL:https://www.apsofdurham.org/event/spring-has-sprung-at-avana-on-broad/
LOCATION:Avana on Broad\, 2335 Broad St\, Durham\, NC\, 27704
CATEGORIES:Adoption Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.apsofdurham.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/0328-Avana-on-Broad.jpg
END:VEVENT
