SUMMARY:Out & About at Bull City Run Club
DESCRIPTION:The arrival of spring means we’re back with our friends at Bull City Running Company! We’ll be there with our running shoes on and a few adoptable dogs for you to meet\, greet\, and fall in love with. Walkers are welcome at BCRC too\, so lace up your duds and come see us!
URL:https://www.apsofdurham.org/event/out-about-at-bull-city-run-club-4/
LOCATION:Bull City Running Company\, 501 Washington Street\, Durham\, NC\, 27701
CATEGORIES:Adoption Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.apsofdurham.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/0401-BCRC.jpg
END:VEVENT
